title: Cincinnati Sides With Pure Romance
url: http://www.bizjournals.com/cincinnati/news/2013/09/11/cincinnati-city-council-backs-pure.html
---

The controversy surrounding Pure Romance's failed efforts to secure tax-incentives for relocating downtown continued this week, after Cincinnati City Council passed a resolution backing the company yesterday. The move comes after Governor John Kasich's office abruptly put an end to the deal with nary an explanation. In the wake, the company is now exploring alternative locations. 

